1
00:00:07,260 --> 00:00:10,700
Have you ever heard about that

2
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:13,580
the cliff of a snow mountain

3
00:00:14,100 --> 00:00:19,220
once fascinated numerous people?

4
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:24,140
Legend has it that,

5
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,940
there were treasures at the peak

6
00:00:27,780 --> 00:00:32,860
but also there was a bottomless chasm hidden over there.

7
00:00:34,460 --> 00:00:37,900
The smart, the fool

8
00:00:37,940 --> 00:00:40,740
and the kind people,

9
00:00:41,380 --> 00:00:47,220
all are familiar to you.

10
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:51,660
On the mountainside, on the cliff,

11
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:54,580
on the cloud,

12
00:00:54,980 --> 00:01:00,100
and in the human world,

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:19,220
snowflakes are drifting profusely and disorderly.

14
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:34,980
Joy of Life Season 1

15
00:01:34,980 --> 00:01:37,900
Episode 4

16
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:22,910
Close the door.

17
00:03:04,470 --> 00:03:05,550
Give out my order.

18
00:03:06,470 --> 00:03:07,720
Tell them to clean up

19
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,600
the servants' kitchen,

20
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:10,670
for Fan Xian to move in.

21
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:11,750
Yes.

22
00:03:18,160 --> 00:03:18,880
Madam.

23
00:03:19,110 --> 00:03:19,880
Still inside?

24
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,320
Yes.

25
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:23,320
There's no sound. It's very quiet.

26
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:31,270
Sizhe! Sizhe!

27
00:03:32,270 --> 00:03:33,000
Wake up!

28
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,880
Mom, ten taels of silver will be enough!

29
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:36,720
You...

30
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:40,080
It's improper for me to go.

31
00:03:40,550 --> 00:03:42,630
Just go to your father's study.

32
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,240
Say that

33
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,960
you're worried that he might be hungry.

34
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,550
Ask him if he wants any pastries.

35
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,080
Take the chance to see

36
00:03:49,270 --> 00:03:50,390
what Fan Xian is doing

37
00:03:50,910 --> 00:03:51,910
in the study.

38
00:03:55,630 --> 00:03:57,390
Mother, you're right.

39
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,960
I'll do as you command.

40
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,190
Take Young Master there.

41
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,270
Yes.

42
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:18,550
So obedient.

43
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:21,000
He's finally made some progress.

44
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:22,950
Lead the way faster!

45
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,070
Yes!

46
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:26,270
It's so late, but my dad hasn't eaten anything yet.

47
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,480
I'm so worried!

48
00:04:30,110 --> 00:04:31,440
Really worried!

49
00:04:31,510 --> 00:04:32,320
Young Master?

50
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,200
Am I silly?

51
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:34,880
Young Master!

52
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:37,600
Madam, Young Master has run away.

53
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:07,660
Fan Jian, Assistant Minister of Ministry of Revenue & Earl Sinan

54
00:05:07,670 --> 00:05:08,550
Feeling anxious after waiting so long?

55
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:13,230
Father, good evening!

56
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,440
To answer your question, I'm not anxious.

57
00:05:20,550 --> 00:05:21,830
After waiting in Danzhou for so many years,

58
00:05:22,230 --> 00:05:23,270
no need to be anxious for a little longer.

59
00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:27,640
It sounds like a complaint.

60
00:05:28,350 --> 00:05:30,270
Should I shed tears

61
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,270
and cry for an hour with you in my arms

62
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,230
to express

63
00:05:33,230 --> 00:05:34,440
my regret?

64
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:35,040
Please don't!

65
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:35,920
I think so, too.

66
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,320
Then let's get down to business.

67
00:05:41,110 --> 00:05:42,880
What kind of person do you want to become?

68
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:47,440
I want to become the richest man in the world,

69
00:05:47,830 --> 00:05:49,550
living a peaceful and romantic life
with many young and beautiful wives.

70
00:05:50,510 --> 00:05:52,320
Sorry, I'm a vulgar man.

71
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,550
How will you build up a fortune?

72
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:55,070
I've already thought about that!

73
00:05:56,070 --> 00:05:57,600
I have a unique technique.

74
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,320
Under high temperatures,

75
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:01,670
I can make something marvelous out of sands

76
00:06:01,670 --> 00:06:03,640
which is much smoother and
more transparent than the crystal.

77
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:05,110
I call it glass.

78
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,390
Once it is made...

79
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,720
Where did you get that?

80
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:16,000
Your mom made it before.

81
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,670
And the technique is mature.

82
00:06:22,230 --> 00:06:23,950
Never mind. I've got something else.

83
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,510
I can use grease

84
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,950
to produce something special

85
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:28,110
which can clean both clothes and human body.

86
00:06:28,110 --> 00:06:29,480
Smooth as grease

87
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,270
with fragrance,

88
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:32,440
it's far better than honey locust and wood ash.

89
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,760
I call it soap.

90
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:44,640
Your mom made that before.

91
00:06:45,110 --> 00:06:46,110
She not only made soap,

92
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,640
but also perfumed soap.

93
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,600
That's fine.

94
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,830
Actually, I've got something else.

95
00:06:51,230 --> 00:06:52,070
Nowadays,

96
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:52,830
besides honey,

97
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:53,760
sweet food are usually made of

98
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:54,880
maltose or malt.

99
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,640
Even saccharose is pretty rough.

100
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,350
I've got a technique

101
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:59,040
to further refine the saccharose into

102
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,720
granulated sugar as white as snow.

103
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,760
And the flavor is excellent.

104
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,670
White granulated sugar.

105
00:07:03,230 --> 00:07:04,950
There are two full jars in the kitchen.

106
00:07:06,670 --> 00:07:08,270
Also made by my mom?

107
00:07:08,510 --> 00:07:11,200
Yes, your mom made it back then.

108
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,110
Why haven't I seen these things

109
00:07:12,110 --> 00:07:13,230
in Danzhou?

110
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:14,510
They are only used by

111
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,040
influential officials

112
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:18,600
and circulated in big cities.

113
00:07:19,790 --> 00:07:20,920
So I'm to blame

114
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:21,760
for living in the rural area.

115
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,230
Do you have any other ideas?

116
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,230
No.

117
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:36,070
Why is my mom always one step ahead of me?!

118
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,670
Your mom ran a firm,

119
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,760
so she had countless fancy ideas.

120
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:44,040
Back then, the scale of her firm

121
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:45,480
was already No.1

122
00:07:45,790 --> 00:07:47,790
in the world.

123
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:50,790
It was the fortune center of the world.

124
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,790
I've heard about that.

125
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,510
Rumor has it that after she died,

126
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,070
the firm was registered under the state treasury.

127
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:56,350
That's not true.

128
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:58,350
It was controlled by the imperial family

129
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,110
and was named Neiku
(Homophone for underwear in Chinese).

130
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:04,270
Who came up with such a vulgar name?

131
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,230
Mind your words!

132
00:08:06,390 --> 00:08:08,480
It was named by His Majesty.

133
00:08:10,670 --> 00:08:13,440
What's so vulgar?

134
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:17,110
Never mind. Go on.

135
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:20,760
Diligent in handling complicated national affairs,

136
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:22,640
His Majesty has no energy

137
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:24,040
to manage Neiku in person.

138
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,230
Therefore,

139
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:27,510
he put Li Yunrui, the Princess Royal,

140
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,760
in charge.

141
00:08:31,670 --> 00:08:33,320
The Princess Royal is in charge of Neiku?

142
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:44,350
She's extremely beautiful

143
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:45,960
and very gentle.

144
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:48,350
Though she's not related to His Majesty by blood,

145
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,280
she's deeply trusted.

146
00:08:50,670 --> 00:08:53,910
And she's not married yet.

147
00:08:54,860 --> 00:08:57,300
Li Yunrui, the Princess Royal of Nanqing

148
00:09:14,350 --> 00:09:15,230
Father,

149
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:18,080
are you into her?

150
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:19,760
Nonsense!

151
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,000
Since we met,

152
00:09:21,350 --> 00:09:23,320
you've talked from the firm to the Princess Royal.

153
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:24,960
You said we would talk about business,

154
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,550
but you only talked about gossips.

155
00:09:27,590 --> 00:09:29,110
Do you know what gossip means?

156
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,550
The Princess Royal

157
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:33,030
has a daughter with Lin Ruofu,

158
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:34,840
the current Prime Minister.

159
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:36,640
You just said

160
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:38,030
she's not married yet.

161
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:40,150
It's a big secret.

162
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,320
You're definitely gossiping!

163
00:09:43,590 --> 00:09:44,960
The Princess Royal's daughter

164
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,150
is named Lin Wan'er.

165
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:49,350
She is the woman

166
00:09:49,670 --> 00:09:50,910
you come to marry.

167
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:52,960
Bastard son and bastard daughter,

168
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:55,790
we're really made for each other.

169
00:09:56,470 --> 00:09:57,640
His Majesty proclaimed that

170
00:09:59,470 --> 00:10:01,110
whoever marries Lin Wan'er

171
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,150
can take over

172
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:05,280
Neiku

173
00:10:05,670 --> 00:10:07,150
from Li Yunrui,

174
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:08,590
the Princess Royal.

175
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:11,320
Chen Pingping and Fei Jie

176
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,840
don't want you to come to the capital now.

177
00:10:13,350 --> 00:10:14,350
I take you here

178
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,030
while they are away.

179
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,230
Because now

180
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,710
is the best chance to get back

181
00:10:19,710 --> 00:10:20,760
your mom's properties

182
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:21,590
and reclaim

183
00:10:21,590 --> 00:10:23,470
what should be yours in the first place.

184
00:10:25,350 --> 00:10:25,790
Here!

185
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:40,790
This is for you.

186
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,880
What's this?

187
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:45,150
The summary of important things of Neiku over the years.

188
00:10:45,350 --> 00:10:46,350
Read it carefully.

189
00:10:46,590 --> 00:10:48,150
It's helpful for you to reclaim the properties.

190
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:48,710
Actually, I...

191
00:10:48,710 --> 00:10:50,440
But you should be more careful.

192
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,670
Neiku is a money tree for the imperial family.

193
00:10:53,030 --> 00:10:55,350
A lot of people don't want you to take over.

194
00:10:56,670 --> 00:10:59,030
My greetings to you, Your Majesty!

195
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:01,760
Arise.

196
00:11:01,910 --> 00:11:03,230
Thank you, Your Majesty!

197
00:11:04,790 --> 00:11:07,400
It's late. What brings you here?
=Empress Dowager of Nanqing=

198
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,550
Your Majesty!

199
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,280
Fan Xian has arrived in the capital.

200
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:15,550
It's the kid Earl Sinan

201
00:11:15,550 --> 00:11:16,520
kept in Danzhou.

202
00:11:19,150 --> 00:11:20,320
Wan'er was sent out of the palace

203
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:22,350
right after I gave birth to her.

204
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:25,030
I've always felt guilty

205
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:27,470
and wanted to find her a good husband.

206
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,550
But Fan Xian is a bumpkin from a remote place

207
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:32,080
with no fame or talent.

208
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:33,910
He's no match for Wan'er!

209
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,790
So, you...

210
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:37,760
I don't want Wan'er to marry him.

211
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:40,200
So the Princess Royal doesn't like the marriage.

212
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:41,710
That's right.

213
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:43,320
She's not happy with it from the start.

214
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:44,440
Then it's over.

215
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:46,200
Without the consent of the mother-in-law,

216
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,150
there will be no marriage.

217
00:11:47,150 --> 00:11:48,710
She has no say

218
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,000
in your marriage with Lin Wan'er.

219
00:11:50,230 --> 00:11:51,320
She's her mom, yet she has no say in this?

220
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,470
For the imperial family,

221
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:54,080
family affection is never the theme.

222
00:11:54,550 --> 00:11:57,790
You want to stop Fan Xian from marrying Wan'er?

223
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,590
Your Majesty, I beg your support!

224
00:12:09,420 --> 00:12:11,100
Hong Sixiang, Head of Eunuchs of Nanqing

225
00:12:17,550 --> 00:12:18,880
Princess Royal.

226
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:22,760
Eunuch Hong,

227
00:12:23,350 --> 00:12:24,440
I'm sorry.

228
00:12:38,470 --> 00:12:39,470
When it comes to the imperial family,

229
00:12:39,790 --> 00:12:42,590
only His Majesty can make the call.

230
00:12:43,110 --> 00:12:46,880
No one cares if you like it or not.

231
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:50,000
That is a warning for you

232
00:12:50,230 --> 00:12:52,470
to never cross the line.

233
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:56,840
Yes.

234
00:13:00,710 --> 00:13:02,080
As long as His Majesty consents,

235
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,760
what others think

236
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:04,590
doesn't matter.

237
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:06,200
But why does His Majesty

238
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:06,960
have to make me

239
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:08,030
marry Lin Wan'er?

240
00:13:08,110 --> 00:13:09,840
His Majesty has four sons.

241
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:11,640
The eldest one is away leading troops.

242
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:13,030
The youngest one is still a child.

243
00:13:13,550 --> 00:13:15,710
Now the Crown Prince and the second prince

244
00:13:16,470 --> 00:13:18,640
are fighting for the throne.

245
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:20,280
How is that relevant to me?

246
00:13:20,710 --> 00:13:23,230
The Princess Royal has supported

247
00:13:23,230 --> 00:13:24,640
the Crown Prince all along.

248
00:13:26,230 --> 00:13:27,150
It's like the imperial wealth

249
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:28,880
is controlled by the Crown Prince.

250
00:13:29,520 --> 00:13:30,400
It's way too dangerous.

251
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:33,200
So the Head of Neiku must be replaced.

252
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,200
Exactly.

253
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:35,880
By taking over Neiku,

254
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:38,150
I practically shake the foundation of the Crown Prince.

255
00:13:39,110 --> 00:13:40,550
This might be the cause of

256
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:43,350
the assassination in Danzhou,

257
00:13:43,470 --> 00:13:44,440
You mean

258
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:46,550
it's the Crown Prince and his followers who tried to kill me.

259
00:13:47,030 --> 00:13:49,760
It's probable with interests concerned.

260
00:13:52,590 --> 00:13:53,590
You've said all these

261
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:55,280
to clear

262
00:13:55,550 --> 00:13:56,880
Liu Ruyu.

263
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:58,910
You don't believe me?

264
00:13:58,910 --> 00:14:00,840
You even drag the Crown Prince into this.

265
00:14:00,880 --> 00:14:01,910
Does it matter if I believe you or not?

266
00:14:05,910 --> 00:14:06,760
Follow me.

267
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,150
Princess Royal.

268
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:24,440
His Majesty wants to see you.

269
00:14:24,670 --> 00:14:26,880
Please come with me.

270
00:14:28,030 --> 00:14:29,150
Just lead the way.

271
00:14:45,260 --> 00:14:47,100
Fan Ruoruo, daughter of Nanqing Earl Sinan Fan Jian

272
00:14:51,260 --> 00:14:52,980
Fan Sizhe, second son of Nanqing Earl Sinan Fan Jian

273
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:54,790
I'm hungry.

274
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,670
Finished talking? Go ahead and take a seat.

275
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:04,840
I have to say this.

276
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:05,640
You don't want to eat,

277
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:07,000
but Fan Xian can be hungry.

278
00:15:19,460 --> 00:15:20,780
Fan Xian, bastard son of Nanqing Earl Sinan Fan Jian

279
00:15:21,620 --> 00:15:22,660
We have important things to discuss. Please leave us.
