Only me?

285
00:15:47,910 --> 00:15:49,000
Get out now!

286
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:49,790
Yes!

287
00:15:52,710 --> 00:15:53,670
Did you send

288
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:56,790
Butler Zhou to Danzhou?

289
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,710
Master, you've known that.

290
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:03,440
Danzhou is so faraway.

291
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:04,960
I thought

292
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:07,000
it would be reassuring to send someone trustworthy

293
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,320
to take care of Xian'er.

294
00:16:08,350 --> 00:16:09,840
He tried to assassinate Fan Xian

295
00:16:10,280 --> 00:16:11,910
in Danzhou.

296
00:16:13,550 --> 00:16:15,230
A...assassinate?!

297
00:16:15,230 --> 00:16:16,000
You don't know that?

298
00:16:16,710 --> 00:16:18,470
I haven't heard from him this month.

299
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:19,790
I've no idea.

300
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:20,840
There won't be any letters.

301
00:16:21,710 --> 00:16:23,640
My mother has sent him onto a fish boat.

302
00:16:23,640 --> 00:16:25,590
He won't get down in recent years.

303
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:30,030
Staying away for all these years,

304
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:33,030
he actually dare betray his master.

305
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:36,080
Thank God Xian'er is all right.

306
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:39,710
Butler Zhou confessed it all.

307
00:16:40,470 --> 00:16:42,440
He had received your secret letter,

308
00:16:43,350 --> 00:16:45,790
asking him to kill Fan Xian

309
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:48,110
with the Investigator's Office.

310
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,150
How come the Investigator's Office is also involved?

311
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:52,960
They also received a fake order.

312
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:55,640
The Investigator's Office only answers to His Majesty.

313
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:57,880
Whoever can insert spies in the Investigator's Office

314
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,960
must be from the imperial family.

315
00:17:00,470 --> 00:17:03,280
And Lady Yi, mother of the youngest prince,

316
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:06,880
happens to be your cousin.

317
00:17:07,800 --> 00:17:09,160
Master, you mean

318
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:10,280
I am the one who wants to kill Fan Xian?

319
00:17:10,430 --> 00:17:11,230
Aren't you?

320
00:17:11,470 --> 00:17:12,310
No, it's not me.

321
00:17:12,310 --> 00:17:13,400
Why not?

322
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,070
I...

323
00:17:14,280 --> 00:17:15,070
Tell him.

324
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:24,830
If I want to kill you,

325
00:17:25,190 --> 00:17:26,110
I'll definitely

326
00:17:26,110 --> 00:17:27,000
find a stranger

327
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:27,710
to do the job.

328
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,590
I'll never ask Butler Zhou to do it.

329
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:31,560
I... I'm not that stupid.

330
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:33,280
Maybe you did it the opposite way.

331
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,760
I have no reason to kill you.

332
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:36,110
You don't want me to inherit the family properties.

333
00:17:36,190 --> 00:17:37,310
No, Fan Xian.

334
00:17:37,310 --> 00:17:38,520
I might be particular about you,

335
00:17:38,520 --> 00:17:39,760
and I might try to suppress you,

336
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:41,000
but I'll never try to kill you.

337
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:41,590
Why?

338
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:43,070
If you die because of me,

339
00:17:43,070 --> 00:17:44,680
Master is sure to

340
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:46,230
drive Sizhe and me out of the Fan mansion.

341
00:17:48,040 --> 00:17:48,640
I...

342
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:49,800
This...

343
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:51,590
Ruoruo.

344
00:17:51,590 --> 00:17:52,710
I think she's made a point.

345
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:55,230
If she wanted to kill you,

346
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:57,230
she wouldn't involve her minion.

347
00:17:58,110 --> 00:17:58,880
Right.

348
00:18:02,520 --> 00:18:03,190
So?

349
00:18:04,280 --> 00:18:05,160
Words alone

350
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:06,160
can't prove anything.

351
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:07,230
I...

352
00:18:08,280 --> 00:18:09,590
You can investigate on your own.

353
00:18:10,590 --> 00:18:11,640
Let's eat first.

354
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:18,350
Here you are!

355
00:18:32,070 --> 00:18:33,430
It's from the Princess Royal.

356
00:18:44,860 --> 00:18:47,060
Li Yunrui, the Princess Royal of Nanqing

357
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:14,590
Your Majesty, the Princess Royal is here.

358
00:19:14,660 --> 00:19:16,420
Emperor Qing, Nanqing's emperor

359
00:19:31,470 --> 00:19:33,040
Don't hold a grudge against the Empress Dowager

360
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:34,710
for that slap on your face.

361
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,040
I just don't want Wan'er

362
00:19:39,040 --> 00:19:40,640
to marry a bumpkin.

363
00:19:41,590 --> 00:19:43,470
You can just say it out!

364
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:44,560
Why ruin

365
00:19:44,560 --> 00:19:46,800
other's reputation instead?

366
00:19:48,350 --> 00:19:49,710
Your Majesty, what do you mean?

367
00:19:50,830 --> 00:19:51,880
I don't understand.

368
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:53,560
Really?

369
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:56,310
Gong Dian!

370
00:19:58,520 --> 00:19:59,230
Yes!
=Gong Dian, Deputy Director of Imperial Guards of Nanqing=

371
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,110
Go find out

372
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:02,470
who sent the maidservants

373
00:20:02,710 --> 00:20:04,070
out for purchasing today.

374
00:20:04,950 --> 00:20:05,830
Yes, Your Majesty!

375
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:24,520
Take a seat.

376
00:20:32,710 --> 00:20:34,110
Come on! Let's eat while the dishes are still hot.

377
00:20:35,070 --> 00:20:35,470
Eat more.

378
00:20:35,470 --> 00:20:36,310
What a feast!

379
00:20:36,430 --> 00:20:37,880
Here, I'll fetch you some soup.

380
00:20:38,190 --> 00:20:38,880
OK.

381
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:39,680
You're so kind!

382
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,920
This is the white gourd clam soup.

383
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:42,110
I especially

384
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:43,430
have the clams delivered.

385
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:45,070
Here! Have a try!

386
00:20:45,830 --> 00:20:46,800
Thank you so much!

387
00:20:46,800 --> 00:20:47,950
Madam, I've never seen such a dish

388
00:20:47,950 --> 00:20:49,040
in Danzhou.

389
00:20:49,310 --> 00:20:50,000
Really?

390
00:20:50,280 --> 00:20:51,110
- Just try it! - How does it taste?

391
00:20:51,110 --> 00:20:51,920
Do you like it?

392
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:53,110
I'm so blessed!

393
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:55,070
- Good! - Terrific!

394
00:20:55,070 --> 00:20:56,350
Madam! Father!

395
00:20:56,520 --> 00:20:58,040
This fish is specially brought here

396
00:20:58,040 --> 00:20:58,640
from Danzhou.

397
00:20:58,640 --> 00:20:59,830
Please try and see how you like it.

398
00:20:59,830 --> 00:21:00,640
OK! Let's taste it!

399
00:21:01,230 --> 00:21:03,310
It looks so yummy. You're so thoughtful.

400
00:21:03,880 --> 00:21:05,040
If you like it,

401
00:21:05,070 --> 00:21:06,520
I'll send you fish regularly from home.

402
00:21:07,070 --> 00:21:08,470
I like it very much. It also smells good.

403
00:21:08,470 --> 00:21:09,310
I'm glad you like it.

404
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:11,880
Master, eat more.

405
00:21:12,710 --> 00:21:13,110
Here!

406
00:21:13,110 --> 00:21:13,590
Madam!

407
00:21:13,830 --> 00:21:15,230
Did you make all the dishes?

408
00:21:15,590 --> 00:21:16,230
Yes, I did.

409
00:21:16,230 --> 00:21:17,680
My dad is so lucky!

410
00:21:18,110 --> 00:21:19,560
I specially made them for you.

411
00:21:19,560 --> 00:21:20,400
Lucky me!

412
00:21:22,040 --> 00:21:23,680
I'd like to learn a few dishes from you in future

413
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:24,760
so that I can cook for you. Is that OK?

414
00:21:24,760 --> 00:21:25,470
No problem!

415
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:27,110
Let me see what I want to learn.

416
00:21:27,110 --> 00:21:28,110
Come on! Try more!

417
00:21:28,110 --> 00:21:28,710
Sister.

418
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:29,400
Here!

419
00:21:29,520 --> 00:21:31,110
I've only been out for a little while.

420
00:21:31,470 --> 00:21:32,310
How come

421
00:21:32,760 --> 00:21:33,880
they suddenly become so close?

422
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:35,470
It's nothing.

423
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:37,310
They just suspect that your mom

424
00:21:37,310 --> 00:21:38,000
tried to kill elder brother.

425
00:21:39,310 --> 00:21:40,430
Come on! Try this!

426
00:21:40,430 --> 00:21:40,830
This!

427
00:21:40,830 --> 00:21:41,520
Let me get it for you.

428
00:21:41,520 --> 00:21:41,920
It's delicious.

429
00:21:42,710 --> 00:21:44,350
Sister, don't you lie to me!

430
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:45,880
It's the truth.

431
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:47,040
Eat with me! I can help myself!

432
00:21:55,520 --> 00:21:56,950
I'm just happy watching you eat.

433
00:21:57,070 --> 00:21:57,880
Then I'll eat more.

434
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:05,470
Here! Here! Here!

435
00:22:05,800 --> 00:22:06,950
Come on! Eat!

436
00:22:06,950 --> 00:22:07,640
OK!

437
00:22:16,040 --> 00:22:16,830
Your Majesty,

438
00:22:17,110 --> 00:22:18,950
Ms. Han from Shanggong Bureau

439
00:22:18,950 --> 00:22:21,040
is the one who arranged for today's purchase.

440
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:21,800
Where is she?

441
00:22:22,800 --> 00:22:25,040
Your Majesty, she has

442
00:22:26,190 --> 00:22:27,070
hung herself.

443
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:49,760
Your Majesty, do you need me to explain

444
00:22:49,760 --> 00:22:51,350
my relationship with that Ms. Han?

445
00:22:52,230 --> 00:22:54,230
No need to make it so clear.

446
00:22:54,590 --> 00:22:55,800
If Your Majesty ask,

447
00:22:56,590 --> 00:22:57,590
I'll answer.

448
00:22:57,760 --> 00:22:58,640
Are you tired?

449
00:22:59,070 --> 00:23:00,310
Resting in the imperial palace all the time,

450
00:23:00,760 --> 00:23:01,710
I don't feel tired.

451
00:23:02,230 --> 00:23:03,430
Good!

452
00:23:03,430 --> 00:23:04,640
Then just sit here and wait!

453
00:23:25,000 --> 00:23:26,040
Your Majesty,

454
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,400
what are we waiting for?

455
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:29,640
A man.

456
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:33,590
May I ask who he is?

457
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:34,800
If it's a court official,

458
00:23:35,230 --> 00:23:36,400
then I'd better excuse myself.

459
00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:37,680
You'll know who he is

460
00:23:38,280 --> 00:23:39,680
when he arrives.

461
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:44,680
Your Majesty, His Highness requests to see you.

462
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:45,590
Let him in.

463
00:23:46,310 --> 00:23:47,760
Look, here he is.

464
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:06,560
Don't just kneel. Say something.

465
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:11,160
It was me who planned

466
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:12,310
the whole maidservants blocking the carriage thing.

467
00:24:12,950 --> 00:24:14,190
I'm willing to take punishments.

468
00:24:14,430 --> 00:24:15,830
I'm really disappointed at you.

469
00:24:17,260 --> 00:24:17,800
Li Chengqian, the Crown Prince of Nanqing

470
00:24:17,800 --> 00:24:18,680
I acknowledge my sin.

471
00:24:18,800 --> 00:24:21,160
Li Yunrui didn't acknowledge anything.

472
00:24:28,470 --> 00:24:29,880
I made the mistake

473
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:30,800
out of temporary confusion.

474
00:24:31,350 --> 00:24:33,040
Reconsidering it now, I feel so ashamed.

475
00:24:33,830 --> 00:24:34,680
Neiku should be managed

476
00:24:35,190 --> 00:24:37,400
by the person pointed by Your Majesty.

477
00:24:37,950 --> 00:24:39,640
I should never act as I think fit.

478
00:24:39,830 --> 00:24:42,950
By taking charge of Neiku,
one can gather the wealth of the world.

479
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:45,190
As the Crown Prince,

480
00:24:45,590 --> 00:24:47,640
you sure have to fight for it.

481
00:24:52,280 --> 00:24:53,920
What really disappointed me

482
00:24:55,040 --> 00:24:57,040
is the means you've adopted.

483
00:25:02,280 --> 00:25:03,310
Let me ask you.

484
00:25:04,110 --> 00:25:05,230
Is there any difference

485
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:06,800
between an imperial blood

486
00:25:06,800 --> 00:25:07,920
and a street civilian?

487
00:25:09,830 --> 00:25:12,070
As different as heaven and earth.

488
00:25:12,190 --> 00:25:13,280
But some may say

489
00:25:14,520 --> 00:25:17,830
they are both

490
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:20,680
ordinary people

491
00:25:21,560 --> 00:25:23,350
with two hands and two eyes.

492
00:25:24,430 --> 00:25:27,040
Your Majesty, that's insane.

493
00:25:27,190 --> 00:25:29,000
What are complicated ethic codes

494
00:25:29,560 --> 00:25:30,760
and strict laws for?

495
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:35,880
For protecting the foundation of the country.

496
00:25:36,310 --> 00:25:37,560
Protecting the foundation of the country?

497
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:41,350
It's for building a high tower

498
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:43,070
in people's heart,

499
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:46,470
so that we can stand high above
the masses with dignity and respect.

500
00:25:46,950 --> 00:25:49,680
Whoever said that should be executed.

501
00:25:49,830 --> 00:25:50,800
Trying to ruin other's name

502
00:25:50,950 --> 00:25:52,430
at the cost of the imperial name,

503
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:55,950
we've become a joke.

504
00:25:57,070 --> 00:26:00,400
With more jokes, there goes the reverence.

505
00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:02,070
Without the reverence,

506
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:05,040
no dignity or respect will be found in people's heart.

507
00:26:05,560 --> 00:26:08,470
Then the tower will collapse, right?

508
00:26:08,470 --> 00:26:10,680
You are ruining our foundation on your own.

509
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:14,520
Your Majesty, I see.

510
00:26:14,520 --> 00:26:15,880
You don't!

511
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:22,350
Just think it over.

512
00:26:28,280 --> 00:26:29,000
Come here.

513
00:26:31,190 --> 00:26:34,520
This is the list of officials

514
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:37,800
to be dismissed these days.

515
00:26:38,280 --> 00:26:39,470
Be prepared for it.

516
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:42,560
See who are on the list.

517
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:45,560
Are your followers on it?

518
00:26:52,190 --> 00:26:54,350
I've also been the Crown Prince.

519
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:58,560
I've fought for what I should.

520
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:01,350
But there is always a line.

521
00:27:03,520 --> 00:27:04,310
Your Majesty!

522
00:27:05,430 --> 00:27:06,430
Just leave!

523
00:27:06,470 --> 00:27:07,110
Your Majesty!

524
00:27:07,110 --> 00:27:07,830
Leave!

525
00:27:42,350 --> 00:27:43,280
Father!

526
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:45,280
I'm leaving for studying.

527
00:27:46,280 --> 00:27:47,470
Me, too.

528
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:51,800
Yes.

529
00:27:59,520 --> 00:28:00,230
Master,

530
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,520
the room for Xian'er

531
00:28:01,520 --> 00:28:03,470
is tidied up.

532
00:28:03,560 --> 00:28:04,680
I'd like to show him around now.

533
00:28:04,680 --> 00:28:05,470
See if he needs anything else.

534
00:28:05,800 --> 00:28:06,800
You may leave first.

535
00:28:07,470 --> 00:28:08,230
I need a word

536
00:28:08,230 --> 00:28:09,470
with him.

537
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:11,710
Yes.

538
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:24,560
You're in the capital city now.

539
00:28:24,950 --> 00:28:26,160
Learn to be cautious

540
00:28:27,190 --> 00:28:28,470
later on.

541
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:30,040
I'm pretty cautious all the time.

542
00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:34,230
How can you call yourself cautious by bring
the assassin of the Investigator's Office

543
00:28:34,520 --> 00:28:35,830
to the capital city.

544
00:28:37,070 --> 00:28:38,230
So you know about Teng Zijing.

545
00:28:38,590 --> 00:28:40,190
The guards escorted you to the capital

546
00:28:40,710 --> 00:28:41,830
are all elites.

547
00:28:42,160 --> 00:28:44,040
You really think they wouldn't notice

548
00:28:44,040 --> 00:28:45,760
when there was one more person.

549
00:28:52,430 --> 00:28:53,040
What's this?

550
00:28:53,280 --> 00:28:54,310
Arrest warrant.

551
00:28:54,760 --> 00:28:56,520
I found it in the files of the Ministry of Penalty.

552
00:29:06,350 --> 00:29:07,470
It's for Teng Zijing.

553
00:29:08,310 --> 00:29:09,230
What crime did he commit?

554
00:29:09,470 --> 00:29:10,950
I don't know, and I don't need to know.

555
00:29:11,190 --> 00:29:12,350
Just be careful of him.

556
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,710
It's an old warrant.

557
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:20,040
Anyway, he's not here now.

558
00:29:21,520 --> 00:29:23,280
Stay away from the Investigator's Office

559
00:29:23,800 --> 00:29:25,920
in future.

560
00:29:26,110 --> 00:29:26,800
Moreover,

561
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:30,350
I will make secret investigations to find out

562
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:32,110
whether the Crown Prince is the one who tried to kill you.

563
00:29:32,110 --> 00:29:34,560
Don't act rashly on your own.

564
00:29:35,520 --> 00:29:36,710
Act rashly?

565
00:29:37,430 --> 00:29:38,640
What can I do?

566
00:29:39,280 --> 00:29:41,400
Can I rush into the Eastern Palace and kill the Crown Prince?

567
00:29:43,950 --> 00:29:45,280
Back then,

568
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:48,710
your mom could really do that!

569
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:50,640
So awesome!

570
00:29:51,310 --> 00:29:53,520
She was bound to no rules of the world.

571
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:56,350
She could always

572
00:29:57,160 --> 00:29:58,640
make unexpected moves.

